Member Function Documentation

void unmanaged::Sched_Event ( struct TEvent *  eventdata  ) 

Sched_Event are used by event stub to post a event. These methods take in parameter the lifo and the first event in this lifo that has been filled with stub parameter before calling these methods. These method unmask interrupt and must be called with interrupt masked.

This methods must be implemented by the scheduler.
